#eNCA speaks to clinical psychologist Nthabiseng Ramothwala. #eNCA #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG -Â The mental health of young people has deteriorated. The latest Mental Health State Of The World report shows South Africa as being the lowest-ranked country when it comes to mental wellness. The report also indicates that education and employment factor highly when it comes to mental wellness. Clinical psychologist Nthabiseng Ramothwala says many people lack the skills to deal with challenges. 